
delete-option-group
*******************


DESCRIPTION
===========

Deletes an existing Option Group.


SYNOPSIS
========

   aws rds delete-option-group
     --option-group-name <value>


REQUIRED PARAMETERS
===================

"--option-group-name"  (string)
   The name of the option group to be deleted.

   Note: You cannot delete default Option Groups.


OPTIONAL PARAMETERS
===================

None
